The paper discusses machine learning algorithms and techniques for discovering and modeling ignorance in data, which is a common concern in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
